  <source>NIH AIDS Clinical Trials Information Service</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To compare the safety, tolerance, and effectiveness of fluconazole and ketoconazole in the
      treatment of candidal esophagitis in immunocompromised patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
